[NOTE] country_alloc_head training killed after 10+ minutes with no epoch output.
Root cause: bounded_knapsack_dp has `for b in range(batch_size):` Python loop — serializes
over batch dimension, making GPU training ~100x slower. Not practical for AWR comparison.
Fix needed: vectorize DP or use a batch-parallel alternative.

